tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE compost_logs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  log_time TIMESTAMP,
  action_type VARCHAR(50),
  user_id INT,
  description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE compost_log (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  log_date DATE,
  activity_description TEXT,
  actor_name VARCHAR(50),
  amendment_type VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE regulatory_compliance (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  regulatory_date DATE,
  regulatory_details TEXT,
  regulatory_entity VARCHAR(50),
  compliance_status BOOLEAN
);
